"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/47100","Department for Transport","false","2014-04-08","<p> </p><p>During March 2014 Belfast Maritime Rescue Coordination Centre (MRCC) was staffed below risk assessed levels on 8 occasions out of 62 shifts.</p><p> </p><p>Where there are specific issues at a MRCC Her Majesty's Coastguard is using the current long established pairing arrangements between MRCCs. This enables each MRCC to be connected to at least one other MRCC which is available to provide mutual support.</p>","Wimbledon","Stephen Hammond","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/47100/answer",,,,,,"2014-04-08T12:00:00.00Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/47100/answer","Biography information for Stephen Hammond","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/47100/answer",,,,,"27","Transport","Transport","2014-04-04","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Transport, how many times the Maritime Rescue Co-ordination Centre, Belfast, was staffed at below risk-assessed levels in March 2014.","false","Biography information for Katy Clark","North Ayrshire and Arran","Katy Clark","195360"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/47101","Department for Transport","false","2014-04-08","<p> </p><p>During March 2014 Stornoway Maritime Rescue Coordination Centre (MRCC) was staffed below risk assessed levels on 6 occasions out of 62 shifts.</p><p> </p><p>Where there are specific issues at a MRCC Her Majesty's Coastguard is using the current long established pairing arrangements between MRCCs. This enables each MRCC to be connected to at least one other MRCC which is available to provide mutual support.</p>","Wimbledon","Stephen Hammond","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/47101/answer",,,,,,"2014-04-08T12:00:00.00Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/47101/answer","Biography information for Stephen Hammond","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/47101/answer",,,,,"27","Transport","Transport","2014-04-04","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Transport, how many times the Maritime Rescue Co-ordination Centre, Stornaway, was staffed at below risk-assessed levels in March 2014.","false","Biography information for Katy Clark","North Ayrshire and Arran","Katy Clark","195361"
